    "We do not have certainty.",
    "After the construction of Google's data centre, Cerrillos could become just one among several other municipalities in Chile served by water trucks in the context of unprecedented drought.",
    "To address this risk, one of the main demands by MOSACAT has been a hydrogeological study that could determine the availability of water in the area.",
    "Unfortunately, such a request has not been addressed by either the municipality of Cerrillos, the municipality-owned water provider SMAPA or Google itself.",
    "The same concern is shared by the Lickan Antay communities in the Atacama Desert."
